#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the Profile Settings Dialog you can also define a maximum archive "
#| "slice size, which limits the slice size even if there would be more space "
#| "left on the target device. This helps to create archive slices which can "
#| "then be later burned on a CD/DVD, etc. If you explicitely limit the size "
